I will update `components/SmithingMinigame.tsx` to implement the requested **Easing Logic (Acceleration)** for the ring and change the miss warning color to **White**.

### Changes
1.  **Logic**: Replaced linear subtraction (`shrinkSpeed`) with time-based quadratic easing (`ringTimer` / `shrinkDuration`).
    *   The ring starts shrinking slowly and accelerates as it gets smaller, simulating gravity/tension.
2.  **Difficulty**: Adjusted difficulty to control the **Duration** (total time to shrink) rather than speed. Higher difficulty = faster shrink time.
3.  **Visuals**: Changed the "Miss Warning" color (when the ring is smaller than the target) from Red to **White** as requested.

```typescript
// Easing Logic
const t = this.ringTimer / this.shrinkDuration;
const ease = t * t; // Quadratic Ease In (Accelerating)
this.currentRadius = this.startRadius * (1 - ease);
```

